。\n还记得在刚组建乐队的那段时间里，我们一起去\n吃过蛋糕的那家店吗？我当时点了奶香烤红薯……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event197-05-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"那个奶香烤红薯超好吃，\n我还想再吃一次，所以在找那家店","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event197-05-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"TORIKO","body":"超好吃的奶香烤红薯吗~\n我不记得了呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"PATO","body":"咖啡厅和蛋糕店的话，学校附近有好多家，\n但我们当时要了开演出庆功会的零花钱后，\n去了不少地方呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"BERRY","body":"而且，LOCK不管去哪家店都会点奶香烤红薯，\n每次都吃得很香，\n所以我们不知道你特别喜欢的是哪一家","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fon